          "text": "32 bits"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "64 bits"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "16 bits",
      "explanation": "The IP header has a 16-bit (2-byte) checksum field located at offset 10-11 in the header.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-2",
      "question": "Which arithmetic is used in Internet checksum calculation?",
      "options": [
